-- Dataset Info --
Content: Ratings (5-star scale) and tags for movies from MovieLens
Size: 100,836 ratings, 3,683 tags, 9,742 movies, 610 users
(This is using the small version of the dataset, could be expanded to work with bigger one later)

Files:

--|ratings.csv: userId, movieId, rating, timestamp (sorted by userId then movieId).

--|tags.csv: userId, movieId, tag, timestamp (sorted by userId then movieId).

--|movies.csv: movieId, title, genres (genres pipe-separated).

--|links.csv: movieId, imdbId, tmdbId (external identifiers).

Data Notes:
_ CSV files, UTF-8 encoded.
_ User and movie IDs are consistent across files.
_ Ratings include half-star increments (0.5â€“5.0).
_ Timestamps are in seconds since Jan 1, 1970 (UTC)

LINK: https://grouplens.org/datasets/movielens/
